body: I should have added, another way to build is from c:\go\src\github.com\docker\docker, run `sh hack/make.sh binary`. That will build docker.exe into bundles\1.11.0-dev\docker.exe. And won't need the autogen part. But will need rsrc installed by the equivalent of these lines from Dockerfile.windows: https://github.com/docker/docker/blob/master/Dockerfile.windows#L94-96
